&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic Co-op Research Assistant to be part of a multidisciplinary Process Development team driving our Adrenal Program forward. In this role, you will take ownership of critical optimization projects focused on 3D cell aggregation, scaling up our culture systems, and onboarding functional bioassays. This is an exciting opportunity for you to work closely with a team of engineers, cell biologists, and preclinical experts to develop scalable cell-therapy platforms that could transform how we treat endocrine diseases.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
