&lt;li&gt;Optimizing 2D and 3D cell culture systems to improve cell viability and function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onboarding and validating new assays supporting downstream, in vivo and histology pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluating 3D culture systems to generate high-quality aggregates, establishing a scalable and cost-effective method.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Planning and executing experimental series semi-independently, including writing study plans, preparing resources, and collecting high-quality technical data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compiling experimental findings into clear summaries, drafting standardized written protocols, and presenting results effectively to key stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing and implementing adrenal cell process improvements to enable clinical manufacturing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting routine cell culture operations, media preparation, and daily laboratory and administrative tasks reliably.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating cross-functionally with team members and other departments to ensure seamless project integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performing human adrenal cell isolations to support the team in building robust cell biobanks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
