&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a highly motivated GMP Facilities Engineer to join our dynamic Technical Operations team in Fremont, California. Reporting to the Chief Technical Officer, or designee, you will be instrumental in evolving our Policy, Procedure and Practice in support of Aspect biosystem’s clinical development programs. You’ll be joining a company committed to developing regenerative medicines that deliver life-changing, functional cures for patients living with serious diseases.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the GMP Facilities Engineer, you will provide essential technical support for the Fremont site’s metrology program and facility operations. This role is a mix of hands-on technical execution and project coordination, ensuring that manufacturing equipment and site utilities (process gases, HVAC, electrical, and mechanical) are calibrated, maintained, and compliant with regulatory expectations and site standards.&lt;/p&gt;
