&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education: &lt;/strong&gt;You hold a Bachelor in Engineering, another relevant discipline or equivalent experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience: &lt;/strong&gt;4-6 years of experience in a regulated industry (Biotech, Pharma, or Med Device), with a strong preference for experience in metrology and facility engineering. We will consider applicants with a mix of industry and educational background.&lt;/li&gt;
