&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Head of Quality Assurance to join Aspect’s technical operations team. Reporting to the Chief Technical Operations Officer, you will be directly responsible for establishing, scaling, and leading the Quality Assurance (QA) team and directing overall GxP compliance for our bioprinted tissue therapeutics. You will be accountable for embedding a culture of quality, integrity, and compliance across the entire product value chain, from early development through clinical manufacturing.&lt;/p&gt;
