&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Histology Co-op to join our Translational Sciences team. You will be an integral part of our team supporting pre-clinical research and histology experimental activities. You will work closely with the histology team to ensure the smooth execution of experimental procedures, inventory management, preparation and imaging of samples.&lt;/p&gt;
